{"tid":1899443,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"遊戲超級大減價 一餐飯價錢入手 Steam 10 款總值過千元遊戲","createTime":"2020-02-26T15:12:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T02:53:25.000Z","uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7875480cbeba0fc0a7384391eaf1cc848f7af2a5","tid":1899443,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T15:12:27.000Z","msg":"遊戲超級大減價 一餐飯價錢入手 Steam 10 款總值過千元遊戲<br />\n<br />\n外國遊戲販賣網站 Fanatical 近日宣佈，推出一個超抵價遊戲組合包「收割者捆綁包2」，只需 4.99 美元 (約 $38 港幣) 即可入手 10 款遊戲的 Steam 激活碼！<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/202002/25/085fc0ad-576f-4576-a470-0a36793b9c1f.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F202002%2F25%2F085fc0ad-576f-4576-a470-0a36793b9c1f.jpeg&h=0c484220&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲販賣網站 Fanatical 宣佈推出「收割者捆綁包2」遊戲特惠包，收錄第一身射擊遊戲《S.T.A.L.K.E.R.》系列三部曲、《星球大戰 絕地武士III：絕地學院》、《星球大戰 絕地武士II：絕地放逐者》、《Day of Infamy》、《模擬城市4 豪華版》、《Eagle Island》、《Override: Mech City Brawl》、《Re-Legion》一共 10 款遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/202002/25/3c718a35e8709f85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F202002%2F25%2F3c718a35e8709f85.jpg&h=edc02b68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這 10 款遊戲總值 $174.9 美元(約 $1,360 港幣)，現在只需要 4.99 美元 (約 $38 港幣) 即可入手 Steam 激活碼，「收割者捆綁包2」優惠期至 3 月 14 日為止，有興趣的玩家不要錯過！<br />\n<br />\nFanatical 商店：<a href=\"https://www.fanatical.com/en/bundle/reaper-bundle-2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fanatical.com%2Fen%2Fbundle%2Freaper-bundle-2&d=dKvfM97HALqNkq2vb6iplBVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=18e2b758\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fanatical.com/en/bundle/reaper-bundle-2</a>"},{"pid":"bc565e09fb5c243cf1293f33751adaddaa1b8524","tid":1899443,"uid":1928,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T15:15:24.000Z","msg":"雖然好平但冇一隻想玩"},{"pid":"4d5dbcf2eefaf857ecdd482835d2bde51787bdc0","tid":1899443,"uid":73143,"like"